			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">In Tanzania, the Fight against Blast Fishing Is Ramping Up</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Explosives offer an effective—and extremely destructive—way to fish.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/scarlett-buckley/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Scarlett Buckley</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						January 19, 2024 | 750 words, about 3 minutes					</aside>
