						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0AIn Tanzania, the Fight against Blast Fishing Is Ramping Up%0D%0AExplosives offer an effective—and extremely destructive—way to fish.%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/in-tanzania-the-fight-against-blast-fishing-is-ramping-up/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



					</ul>
